name: RMNibLoadedView
summary: RMNibLoadedView nib Loader view class that respects IBInspectable / IBDesignable options.
description:
upport for views loaded from NIB/XIB files from code and interface builder.
Respects IBInspectable / IBDesignable options. Inspired by https://bitbucket.devops.nonprod.empf.local/scm/react/nib-loaded-views.
